snippet.title: Super Smash Bros. Ultimate - E3 2018 - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Legendary game worlds and fighters collide in Super Smash Bros. Ultimate. 

New fighters…check.

New stages…check.

Every fighter that was ever featured in the series…
…check.

Prepare yourself for the ultimate showdown.

Super Smash Bros. Ultimate arrives December 7, 2018! https://www.smashbros.com/en_US/index.html

Follow Nintendo E3 Coverage! http://e3.nintendo.com
